How to install XMind

First Download, 
* Download this link http://www.xmind.net/xmind/downloads/xmind-8-beta-linux_amd64.deb

Second, go to download file location and open terminal

* sudo dpkg -i xmind-8-beta-linux_amd64.deb

If u see this error at terminal, 
dpkg : dependency problems prevent configuration...
dpkg : error processing package xmind(--install):...

Please type at terminal , 
* sudo apt --fix-broken install

You can reference at youtube, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hE-QdcX5yQo




